```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Payments
    participant Ledger
    participant Flutterwave
    participant Notifications

    Client->>Gateway: POST /payments/quotes
    Gateway->>Payments: Create quote
    Payments-->>Gateway: Quote with FX markup
    Gateway-->>Client: Quote response

    Client->>Gateway: POST /payments/transfers (Idempotency-Key)
    Gateway->>Payments: Create transfer
    Payments->>Ledger: reserve(reference)
    Ledger-->>Payments: Pending transaction id
    Payments->>Flutterwave: initiate payout
    Flutterwave-->>Payments: Accepted + providerRef
    Payments->>Ledger: emit TransferPending event
    Payments->>Notifications: Publish pending notification
    Payments-->>Gateway: Transfer accepted
    Gateway-->>Client: 202 Accepted
```
